quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,160,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵatesile toba ni kwilanya (yaŵawatanganyagayo) ni kusalichisya (yaŵasisagayo), basi ŵanganyao ni ŵachinapochele toba jao, soni Une ni Jwakupochela nnope toba, Jwachanasa channope."
  2,161,"Chisimu aŵala ŵakanile nikwikanila kuwa ali makafili, ŵanganyao malweso ga Allah, Achimalaika ni ŵandu wosope gali pa jamanjao."
  2,162,"Mwele (mmalweso ga ku Motogo) chakaŵe ŵandamo, ilagasyo ngaija kupungusyidwa kwa jamanjao, soni ŵanyao ngaaja kupedwa lipesa."
  3,100,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Naga nkwika mwakulipikanila likuga line mu ŵandu ŵaŵapedwile chitabu, cham'buchisye ku ukafili panyuma pakulupilila kwenu."
  3,101,"Ana chim'be makafili chanti uli kutendaga ma Ȃya ga Allah gakusoomedwa kukwenu nombenajo Ntenga ﷺ ali chilikati chenu? Sano jwachalikamulile chenene mwa Allah, nikuti pamasile paajongoleledwe kwitala lyagoloka."
  3,102,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Mun'jogopani Allah kun'jogopa kusyesyene, soni nkaika mwa kuwa ikaŵeje n'di Asilamu."
  4,40,"Chisimu Allah jwangatenda lupuso (ku iwumbe Yakwe atamuno pachitendo chamwana chanti chisawu) usito wa lunyilili, sano nachiŵaga chambone, akasachitupiyaga nikupeleka kuumila Kukwakwe malipilo gamakulungwa nnope."
  4,41,"Nambi ichiŵa uli ndema jatuchiika najo mboni kutyochela mu nkutula uliwose (jakuutendela umboni nkutulao), nikwika namwe (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) kuŵa mboni pa ŵanganyaŵa?"
  4,42,"Lyele lisikulyo aŵala ŵaŵakufuulu, ni kunnyosya Ntenga ﷺ chachilajila yanti: Bolaga likagambe kwasimasya litaka (ningasyuka soni), ni ngasakombola kunsisa Allah liloŵe lililyose (lyakwamba yaŵapanganyisye)."